"title": "2021: Jesus Christ, faithfulness of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "2021: jesus christ, faithfulness of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The total reliability and constancy of Jesus Christ is shown in his personal character, and made known by his words and works.</p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's faithfulness is seen in his character</h2>\n<h3>He is faithful by nature</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:11\">REV 19:11</a></strong> <em>A description of the exalted Christ.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:5\">REV 1:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:14\">REV 3:14</a></p>\n<h3>The promised Messiah is faithful</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:5\">ISA 11:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:3\">ISA 42:3</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ is faithful because he never changes</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:8\">HEB 13:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:11-Heb1:12\">HEB 1:11–1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:26-Ps102:27\">PSA 102:26–102:27</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ is faithful because he is the truth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:14\">JHN 1:14</a></strong> <em>“grace” and “truth” are often associated in Hebrew with love and faithfulness.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:17\">JHN 1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:6\">JHN 14:6</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's faithfulness demonstrated in his obedience</h2>\n<h3>He is faithful to his Father</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:6\">HEB 3:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:49\">LUK 2:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:30\">JHN 5:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:38\">JHN 6:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:29\">JHN 8:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:31\">JHN 14:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:2\">HEB 3:2</a></p>\n<h3>He kept faithfully to his work</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:43\">LUK 4:43</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:38\">MRK 1:38</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:34\">JHN 4:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:4\">JHN 9:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:27\">JHN 12:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:4\">JHN 17:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:30\">JHN 19:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:17-Heb2:18\">HEB 2:17–2:18</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's faithfulness is seen in his words</h2>\n<h3>In his predictions about events</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:28\">MAT 16:28</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:27\">LUK 9:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:1\">MRK 9:1</a> <em>This prediction could refer to either Jesus Christ's transfiguration or his ascension</em>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:2\">MAT 24:2</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:2\">MRK 13:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:6\">LUK 21:6</a> <em>This prediction was fulfilled in A.D. 70 when the Romans destroyed Jerusalem and the temple.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:2\">MAT 21:2</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:2\">MRK 11:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:30\">LUK 19:30</a> <em>finding a donkey and her colt</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:21\">MAT 26:21</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:18\">MRK 14:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:21\">LUK 22:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:21\">JHN 13:21</a> <em>Jesus Christ's betrayer</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:34\">MAT 26:34</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:30\">MRK 14:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:34\">LUK 22:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:38\">JHN 13:38</a> <em>Peter's denial</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:20\">JHN 16:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:18-John21:19\">JHN 21:18–21:19</a></p>\n<h3>In his promises about eternal life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:24\">JHN 5:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:28-Matt19:29\">MAT 19:28–19:29</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:29-Mark10:30\">MRK 10:29–10:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:29-Luke18:30\">LUK 18:29–18:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:43\">LUK 23:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:47\">JHN 6:47</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:53-John6:54\">JHN 6:53–6:54</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:51\">JHN 8:51</a></p>\n<h3>In his promise of authority for believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:20\">MAT 17:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:19\">MAT 16:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:18\">MAT 18:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:21\">MAT 21:21</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:23\">MRK 11:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:18-Matt28:19\">MAT 28:18–28:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:19\">LUK 10:19</a></p>\n<h3>In his promise about the Holy Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:26\">JHN 14:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:49\">LUK 24:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:16\">JHN 14:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:26\">JHN 15:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:7\">JHN 16:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:4\">ACT 1:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:8\">ACT 1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:38-Acts2:39\">ACT 2:38–2:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:44-Acts10:46\">ACT 10:44–10:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:5\">ROM 5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:7\">1CO 12:7</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's promises about the future are faithful</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:2-John14:3\">JHN 14:2–14:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:27\">MAT 16:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:64\">MAT 26:64</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:28\">JHN 14:28</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ is faithful to believers in all circumstances</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:13\">2TI 2:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:20\">MAT 18:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:20\">MAT 28:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:9\">JHN 17:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:9-Acts18:10\">ACT 18:9–18:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:3\">2TH 3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:23\">HEB 10:23</a></p>",
